### Lib (`src/lib/`)
- `actions/contacts.ts` ‚Äî Server actions: getContacts, getContact, createContact, updateContact, deleteContact
- `roadmap-data.ts` ‚Äî getRoadmapSpec, getRoadmapsForProducts, getAllRoadmapSpecs
- `auth.ts` ‚Äî getAuthUser, requireAdmin
- `supabase/server.ts` ‚Äî createClient (server), createAdminClient
- `supabase/client.ts` ‚Äî createClient (browser)
- `supabase/middleware.ts` ‚Äî updateSession (auth guard)
- `db/types.ts` ‚Äî Database/Contact/UserProfile TypeScript types

### Types (`src/types/`)
- `roadmap.ts` ‚Äî RoadmapV2, SalesStep, SALES_STEPS (8 steps)
- `index.ts` ‚Äî Product, WordTrack, NavItem

## Sales Step IDs (in order)

`add_contact` ‚Üí `opening` ‚Üí `discovery` ‚Üí `presentation` ‚Üí `samples` ‚Üí `objections` ‚Üí `closing` ‚Üí `followup`

## Database Table: `d2c_contacts`

Key columns: `user_id`, `product_ids text[]`, `first_name`, `last_name`, `email`, `phone`, address fields, `current_step`, `opening_types jsonb`, `questions_asked jsonb`, `objections_encountered jsonb`, `closing_techniques jsonb`, `sample_sent`, `sample_products text[]`, `outcome`, `follow_up_day`

## Environment Variables

`NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`, `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY`

## Conventions

- Use **shadcn/ui** components for all UI
- Use **Server Actions** (not API routes) for data mutations
- All files go in `src/` ‚Äî never create files at project root
- Product pages are reference-only; sales flow lives at `/sales`
- Roadmap JSON files are the single source of truth for sales scripts
- Update `README.md` before every commit
